    {
      "version": "v1",
      "kind": "AssistantMessage",
      "data": {
        "message_id": "ab006f41-3c04-45a6-86de-423ebefae87d",
        "content": [
          {
            "kind": "text",
            "data": ""
          },
          {
            "kind": "toolUse",
            "data": {
              "toolUseId": "tooluse_46NUg2wdgRYPW5KXZ4LjY2",
              "name": "write",
              "input": {
                "__tool_use_purpose": "Write icon audit markdown report to journal folder",
                "command": "create",
                "path": "/workspaces/rubani/journal/icon-audit.md",
                "content": "# Icon Audit — Rubani\n\n**Date:** 2026-05-05  \n**Status:** No external icon library in use. All icons are hand-coded inline SVG or Unicode emoji/symbols.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Type | Count (distinct) | Notes |\n|------|-----------------|-------|\n| Inline SVG | ~20 distinct shapes | Duplicated across templates with no shared component |\n| Emoji | ~20 distinct emoji | Used for categories, status, UI affordances |\n| Unicode symbols | `★` `☆` `✓` `✕` `✗` `⟳` `›` `⚠` | Text-based, no SVG |\n\nNo icon font (Font Awesome, Bootstrap Icons, etc.) and no icon component library (Heroicons, Lucide, Feather, Phosphor, Tabler) is loaded anywhere.\n\n---\n\n## Inline SVG Icons\n\nEach SVG is a 24×24 viewBox stroke icon, hand-pasted inline. The same shape often appears in multiple templates with different `width`/`height` and `stroke` colour attributes.\n\n| Icon | Shape description | Used in |\n|------|------------------|---------|\n| **Dashboard / Grid** | 4 equal squares | `base_dashboard.html` (sidebar), `base.html` (nav) |\n| **Orders / Clipboard** | Clipboard with rect | `base_dashboard.html` (sidebar), `dashboard/home.html` (KPI) |\n| **Products / Box** | 3D box / package | `base_dashboard.html` (sidebar) |\n| **Categories / Grid-4** | 4 squares with bottom bar | `base_dashboard.html` (sidebar) |\n| **Customers / Users** | Two person silhouettes | `base_dashboard.html` (sidebar) |\n| **Search / Magnifier** | Circle + diagonal line | `base.html` (nav), `dashboard/products.html`, `dashboard/orders.html`, `dashboard/customers.html` |\n| **Cart / Bag** | Shopping bag outline | `base.html` (nav) |\n| **User / Person** | Circle head + shoulders | `base.html` (nav), `accounts/profile.html` |\n| **Revenue / Dollar** | Vertical line + S-curve | `dashboard/home.html` (KPI) |\n| **Cart / Trolley** | Trolley path | `dashboard/home.html` (KPI) |\n| **Warning / Triangle** | Triangle with exclamation | `dashboard/home.html` (KPI, notification) |\n| **Chevron Left** | `<` arrow | `dashboard/product_detail.html` (back), `dashboard/order_detail.html` (back) |\n| **Arrow Left** | `←` path | `orders/order_detail.html` (back) |\n| **Info / Circle-i** | Circle with `i` | `dashboard/product_detail.html`, `dashboard/product_add.html` |\n| **Checkmark** | Polyline tick | `dashboard/product_detail.html`, `dashboard/product_add.html`, `dashboard/products.html`, `dashboard/order_detail.html` |\n| **Edit / Pencil** | Pencil path | `dashboard/product_detail.html`, `dashboard/products.html`, `accounts/profile.html` (×2) |\n| **Upload / Arrow-up** | Arrow up from tray | `dashboard/product_detail.html`, `dashboard/product_add.html` |\n| **Download / Arrow-down** | Arrow down to tray | `dashboard/analytics.html` |\n| **Trash / Delete** | Bin with lines | `dashboard/products.html` |\n| **Close / X** | Two crossing lines | `dashboard/products.html` (inline JS) |\n| **List view** | Horizontal lines with dots | `dashboard/orders.html` |\n| **Column / Bar chart** | Three vertical rects | `dashboard/orders.html` |\n| **Logout / Arrow-right-out** | Door with arrow | `accounts/profile.html` |\n| **Chevron right (small)** | `›` polyline | `store/sections/categories_v2.html` (tile arrow) |\n| **Decorative SVG blobs** | Abstract shapes/circles | `store/sections/categories_v2.html` (category tile backgrounds) |\n| **Confirmation tick (large)** | Large checkmark circle | `orders/confirmation.html` |\n\n---\n\n## Emoji Icons\n\n| Emoji | Meaning / Context | Used in |\n|-------|------------------|---------|\n| 🛍️ | Product image placeholder | `store/_product_card.html`, `store/sections/hero_v1.html`, `orders/cart.html`, `orders/checkout.html`, `store/sections/custom_spotlight_v1.html`, `dashboard/homepage_editor.html` |\n| 🛒 | Empty cart state | `orders/cart.html` |\n| 📦 | Order / package placeholder | `orders/order_detail.html`, `dashboard/orders.html`, `accounts/order_history.html` |\n| 🔥 | Deal / sale badge | `base.html` (nav link), `store/sections/hero_v1.html`, `dashboard/homepage_editor.html`, `dashboard/product_detail.html` |\n| ★ / ☆ | Star rating (filled / empty) | `store/_product_card.html`, `store/product_detail.html`, `store/sections/testimonials_v1.html`, `store/sections/hero_v1/v2/v3.html` |\n| 🗂️ | Category fallback (no icon/image) | `store/sections/categories_v3/v4/v5/v6.html` |\n| 🏷️ | Category fallback in dashboard | `dashboard/categories.html` |\n| 📱 | \"Phones\" demo category | `store/sections/categories_v3/v4/v5/v6.html` (static demo rows) |\n| 💻 | \"Laptops\" demo category | same as above |\n| 🎧 | \"Audio\" demo category | same as above |\n| 🏠 | \"Smart Home\" demo category | same as above |\n| 📍 | Physical address (footer) | `base.html` |\n| 📞 | Phone number (footer) | `base.html` |\n| ✉ | Email (footer) | `base.html` |\n| 💬 | Chat / WhatsApp CTA | `orders/confirmation.html` |\n| 💳 | Card payment option | `orders/checkout.html` |\n| 📱 | M-Pesa payment option | `orders/checkout.html` |\n| 🔒 | Mock/secure payment notice | `orders/checkout.html` |\n| 🔁 | Repeat purchase / cohort | `dashboard/analytics.html` |\n| 🚨 | Critical stock alert | `dashboard/analytics.html` |\n| ⚠ | Action needed alert | `dashboard/analytics.html` |\n| 🏙 | Nairobi county | `dashboard/analytics.html` |\n| 🌿 | Kiambu county | `dashboard/analytics.html` |\n| 👁 | Visibility toggle / visible label | `dashboard/homepage_editor.html`, `dashboard/product_add.html`, `dashboard/product_detail.html` |\n| 🙈 | Hidden state (visibility toggle) | `dashboard/homepage_editor.html` |\n| 🚀 | Product add \"launch\" step indicator | `dashboard/product_add.html` |\n| 💰 | Discount hint | `dashboard/product_add.html` |\n| 🛍 | Products empty state (no trailing variation selector) | `dashboard/products.html` |\n\n---\n\n## Unicode Symbol Icons\n\n| Symbol | Meaning | Used in |\n|--------|---------|---------|\n| `✓` | Success / confirmed / completed step | `store/product_detail.html`, `orders/confirmation.html`, `store/sections/newsletter_v